spec_data.Name: php-pear-File-Passwd
spec_data.Description:
Provides methods to manipulate and authenticate against standard Unix,
SMB server, AuthUser (.htpasswd), AuthDigest (.htdigest), CVS pserver
and custom formatted password files.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 08:32:43 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Manipulate many kinds of password files
